{"tid":491500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那趣聞：10元任裝爆谷　水桶油漆桶全出動","createTime":"2017-12-06T14:43:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-09T14:27:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":149,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4ab0227887c74e4388b3668fe421f61c62fa65","tid":491500,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"12月06日(三) 19:01   <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/photo/bkncn-20171206190141845-1206_05011_001_04p.jpg?20171206190501\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20171206190141845-1206_05011_001_04p.jpg%3F20171206190501&h=b39e4b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n浙江杭州有戲院周二（5日）舉行活動，顧客只需付10元人民幣，即可到戲院附設小食店內任食爆谷，甚至可自備容器「想裝多少，就裝多少」。不少市民聞訊蜂擁而至，除小型的膠袋和曲奇罐外，甚至有人帶了水桶、油漆桶等前來。 <br />\n<br />\n雖然當日不少民眾都「滿載而歸」，但有網民直言他們只是貪小便宜，「取那麼多，真的吃得完嗎？」、「抱這麼大個桶，最後扔的應該有一半以上」。更有人留言嘲諷稱：「怎麼不把爆谷機器和原材料抱回家，想吃多少想甚麼時候吃都可以」。"},{"pid":"c5ab5bf621962ba50aa0682215331839f2c9a559","tid":491500,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206190141845-1206_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171206%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171206190141845-1206_05011_001.html&d=eN%2BMjmt9Z7aR3emPvjHrhEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5e077ecb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171206/mobile/bkncn-20171206190141845-1206_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e6a1556ed2737d650b35972a48bd3d567f0df9b7","tid":491500,"uid":30169,"like":269,"dislike":8,"score":261,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"垃圾民族"},{"pid":"02e5c15e32c95b20dd50e07d7cca12e8000cc65c","tid":491500,"uid":14250,"like":81,"dislike":1,"score":80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T14:46:48.000Z","msg":"一陣搞到大家都冇得食，中國人最叻咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=